    <briefdescription>
<para>Singleton manager that holds the global <ref refid="classDali_1_1Ui_1_1UiConfig" kindref="compound">UiConfig</ref> instance. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><ref refid="classDali_1_1Ui_1_1Integration_1_1UiConfigManager" kindref="compound">UiConfigManager</ref> provides process-wide access to the <ref refid="classDali_1_1Ui_1_1UiConfig" kindref="compound">UiConfig</ref>. Configuration values should be read directly from the <ref refid="classDali_1_1Ui_1_1UiConfig" kindref="compound">UiConfig</ref> returned by <ref refid="classDali_1_1Ui_1_1Integration_1_1UiConfigManager_1a2c6e612a48923d9bbf0664f7941fd193" kindref="member">GetConfig()</ref>.</para>
<para>Must be initialized exactly once before the application main loop starts. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
